        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", but one by one, tender sympathy going out from Him in each case. Intrinsically probable, and worth noting. This trait in Lk. is in its own way as valuable as Mt.’s citation from Isaiah (",
